- Come on, guys.

136
00:07:48,642 --> 00:07:51,471
- Just say HLH.

137
00:07:51,514 --> 00:07:53,473
- Uh, HLH is extremely rare.

138
00:07:53,516 --> 00:07:54,909
- I know. I mean, we barely

139
00:07:54,952 --> 00:07:56,519
