- Why?

153
00:08:25,287 --> 00:08:26,593
- How can I help?

154
00:08:34,818 --> 00:08:36,732
- Conco's at 23! LB!

155
00:08:36,777 --> 00:08:38,866
Buy! Buy!
- Buy!

156
00:08:38,909 --> 00:08:40,607
Buy!

157
00:08:40,650 --> 00:08:43,131
Today
was insane, man.

158
