me a mermaid, okay?

237
00:12:28,573 --> 00:12:30,140
I'll be right back.

238
00:12:36,364 --> 00:12:38,801
Hi, Yulia. I'm Dr. Goodwin.

239
00:12:38,845 --> 00:12:40,977
